<i>adverb</i>: 되레 [되ː레/뒈ː레], 도리어 [도리어] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>되레 [되ː레/뒈ː레]</dt><br>
<dd>instead; on the contrary</dd><br>
<dd>기대했던 것이나 일반적인 생각과는 반대되거나 다르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being against or contrary to one's expectation or a general assumption.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도리어 [도리어]</dt><br>
<dd>instead; on the contrary</dd><br>
<dd>기대했던 것이나 일반적인 것과 반대되거나 다르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being against or contrary to one's expectation or a general assumption.</dd><br>
</li>
